item.title: What is Structured Water™
item.description:
What is Structured Water™

Structured Water is created by the natural action of water in nature. http://www.NaturalActionTechnologies.com The natural action of water tumbling over rocks, down waterfalls, flowing through twists and turns as it actively descends a mountain actually structures water. Water molecules are free to move and "dance with nature" in an energetically alive, fresh and vibrant manner.
